Installing FIREBALL
===================
1. Enter into directory src

2. Edit Makefile.in and select the appropiated MACHINE variable.
   Also select the other parameters such as type of theory, etc. 
   There is a GENERIC version that fit many common environments both
   with intel and gcc compilers

3. Compile the executables:
   make begin.x
   make create.x
   make fireball.x

